dip.judge.parser

Class JudgeOrderParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • dip.judge.parser.JudgeOrderParser

  • public class JudgeOrderParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Parses Move, Retreat, and Adjustment phase orders.

    This assumes that orders never span lines.
